                <h1 class="activity-page-title">Green &amp; Climate-Proof Your Block</h1>
                <h2 class="activity-page-question">Why do this?</h2>
                <p class="activity-page-question-answer">Create a street garden in traffic circles or even on the street
                    in front of your place by planting vegetation that you like. Creating this type of green
